    <item>
      <title>苹果计划基于人工智能对 Siri 进行全面改造，以控制单个应用程序功能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/apple-ios-18-siri-ai-update-will-let-users-control-features-in-apps-with-voice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司正计划以更先进的人工智能彻底改造其 Siri 虚拟助手，此举将允许用户通过语音控制单个应用程序的功能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/apple-ios-18-siri-ai-update-will-let-users-control-features-in-apps-with-voice</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:54:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国正在放缓 Nvidia、AMD 对中东的 AI 芯片出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-officials-rein-in-ai-chip-sales-to-middle-east-by-nvidia-amd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国官员已放缓向英伟达公司和超威半导体公司等芯片制造商发放向中东大规模出货人工智能加速器的许可证，同时对该地区人工智能发展进行国家安全审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-officials-rein-in-ai-chip-sales-to-middle-east-by-nvidia-amd</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业 AI 的崛起 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/the-rise-of-enterprise-ai-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 Salesforce 销售额不及预期，股价暴跌再次引发人们对在 AI 领域落后的担忧，彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 与 C3.ai 首席执行官 Tom Siebel 一起分析了企业 AI 的前景。此外，当这位科技领袖面临帝国威胁时，让我们看看埃隆·马斯克的世界，以及一家公司如何希望为无线运营商实现 100% 的服务覆盖。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/the-rise-of-enterprise-ai-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 18:23:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊获监管机构批准扩大美国无人机服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/amazon-to-expand-us-drone-service-after-getting-regulator-s-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司的 Prime Air 无人机项目已获得美国监管机构的批准，允许设备在飞行员的视线之外飞行，从而增加飞行范围并让更多客户享受该服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/amazon-to-expand-us-drone-service-after-getting-regulator-s-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 11:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠普 PC 销售恢复，股价创 2015 年分拆以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hp-reports-increased-computer-sales-with-optimism-rising-for-ai-pcs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠普公司 (HP Inc.) 公布其个人电脑销量两年来首次增长，创下 2015 年与姊妹公司惠普企业 (Hewlett Packard Enterprise) 分拆以来的最大涨幅，这是市场期待已久的反弹的乐观信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hp-reports-increased-computer-sales-with-optimism-rising-for-ai-pcs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:17:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前景不佳导致 Salesforce 股价暴跌 2008 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Salesforce Inc. 预计季度销售增幅将创历史新低，股价出现近 20 年来最大跌幅，这再次引发了人们对该公司将在人工智能热潮中落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
